race.description: Mountain View Hotel Tooraweenah Cup Handicap
race.comment: DERVINIA (4) got well back over 1400m at Parkes last time and never threatened when tenth. Clayton Gallagher gets the best out of this five-year-old and assess on the good win three-back at Dubbo. THE HULKBUSTER (10) was in contention on the turn and progressed nicely last start to finish a close third over 1300m at Gunnedah. Will appreciate the claim and shapes as a leading player. BIG SHOT LEGEND (2) was in the money first up at this track then could only manage tenth last time out over 1300m at Gunnedah. Finds an easier race and the claim helps. Minor place contender. ST ROY (15) showed good improvement last start and appears the next in line.
